   <topic>A5_DESIGN_BITMAP Function</topic>
   <syntax>L a5_design_bitmap([C bitmap_name ])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>bitmap_name</name>
         <description>Character</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
   <description>Public user defined function.</description>
   <discussion>
The A5_DESIGN_BITMAP() function displays the Create Global Bitmap dialog box, which allows you to import a bitmap from a file or paste it from the clipboard.

   </discussion>
  
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
